title: 2 Chainz Announces "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" Release Date
text:
Home > Music > 2 Chainz Announces "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" Release Date 2 Chainz Announces "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" Release Date 2 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Jan 15, 2017 at 11:50pm 2 Chainz will release "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" in April. 
2 Chainz had a career year in 2016. He turns 40 this upcoming September, but he's at the top of his game. Rap game R.A. Dickey. 
Two weeks ago, he announced Pretty Girls Like Trap Music , his first project of 2017. Sunday evening, he announced the release date: April 7th. 
He announced the news on Instagram, in the caption of a photo in which he vibes in the studio with Drake and someone who may or may not be Jahkoy. 
Tity Boi has yet to reveal any information about the nature of Pretty Girls Like Trap Music . Is it his third album? Despite all the great 2 Chainz music 2016 produced, it did not produce a full-length solo album. Stay tuned...
